div.white_wrapper_tl {
    width: 100vw;
    margin: 0;
} 
div#content_top_shadow {
    width: 100vw;
}
div#header {
    width:100%;
    height: 50vh;
    background: black;
}
div#header div.top_header {
    /*height: 50px;*/
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    padding: 1vh 5vw;
    
}
div#header div.top_header ul.quick_menu {
    width: 70vw;
    height: auto;
}
ul.quick_menu li.home {
    float: left;
    padding: 0px 10px;
    border-right: 0.5px solid #d6d2d2;
}

ul.quick_menu li {
    float: left;
    padding: 0px 10px;
    border-right: 0.5px solid #d6d2d2;
    background: none;
}
ul.quick_menu li a {
    color: white;
    font-size: 11px;
}
div#header div.top_header ul.languages {
    background: none;
    margin-left: 10px;
    padding-left: 0;
}
div#header div.top_header ul.languages li span {
    color: white;
    font-size: 11px;
    border-right: 1px solid #d6d2d2;
    padding-right: 10px;
}
div#header div.top_header ul.languages li a {
    color: white;
    font-size: 11px;
}

/* NAVIGATION */

div#navigation {
    margin-top: 7.5vh;
    width: 100vw;
    margin-left: 5px;
    margin-right: 10px;
} 
div#navigation table {
    width: 98vw;
}
div#navigation td {
    border-right: 1px solid black;
    height: 10vh;
}
div#navigation td.first {
    border-right: 1px solid black;
    height: 10vh;
}
div#navigation td.first a{
    padding-top: 0px;
    background: #3d3d3d;
    height: 13vh;
}
div#navigation a span {
    background: #3d3d3d;
    height: auto;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: bold;
    padding-top: 10px;
    color: #e6e6e6;
}
div#navigation td.first a span {
    background: #3d3d3d;
    padding-top: 10px;
    
}
div#navigation td a{
    padding-top: 0px;
    height: 13vh;
    background: #3d3d3d;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
}
div#header div.top_header {
    margin: 0px 30px 0px 20px;
}

div#header div.top_header {
    margin: 0;
    width: 90vw;
}

/* BODY CONTENT */

div#content_top_shadow div#content {
    width: 100vw;
}
div#content_top_shadow div#content div.two_cols_wrapper {
    width: 80vw;
}

/* MORE INFORMATION */

div#more_information {
    width: auto;
    margin-left: -10px;
}
div#more_information div.box div.top div h4.title {
    width: auto;
    background: #2e2b2b;
    font: normal 15px Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;
    color: #ededed;
    font-weight: bold;
}
div#more_information div.rate div.top div {
    width: 17vw;
}
div#more_information div.rate div.top div ul li {
    font-size: 15px;
}
div#more_information div.box {
    background: #e6e6e6;
    width: 17vw;
}
div#more_information div.box div.top {
    background: #e6e6e6;
}
div#more_information div.box div.top div {
    background: #e6e6e6;
}
div#more_information div.box div.top div ul li {
    border-bottom: 0px solid #b3aead;
    margin: 5px 0px;
}
div#more_information div.box div.top div a {
    color: black;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 20px;
}

/* SIDEBAR */

div#sidebar {
    width: 17vw;
    margin-left: 1vw;
}
div#sidebar div.box {
    background: #e6e6e6;
}
div#sidebar div.box div.top{
    background: #e6e6e6;
}
div#sidebar div.box div.top div {
    background: #e6e6e6;
    width: auto;
}
div#sidebar div.box div.top div h4.title{  
    background: #2e2b2b;
    font: normal 15px Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;
    color: #ededed;
    font-weight: bold;
    width: auto;
}
div#sidebar div.box div.top div ul li {
    padding: 6px 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
}
div#sidebar div.box div.top div a {
    color: black;
    font-size: 15px;
}
div#sidebar div.white div.top div ul li {
    border-bottom: 0px solid #b3aead;
    margin: 5px 0px;
}

/* MAIN */

div#main {
    margin-left: 2.3vw;
    margin-top: 3vh;
    width: 55vw;
}
div#main div.tabbed_information div.tabs {
    text-align: center;
}
div#main div.tabbed_information div.tabs a.active {
    background: #2e2b2b;
    color: #ededed;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: bold;
    width: 100%;
}
div#main div.tabbed_information div.tabs a {
    background: #2e2b2b;
    color: #ededed;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: bold;
}
div#main div.tabbed_information div.items {
    background: #e6e6e6;
}
div#main div.tabbed_information div.items div.top {
    background: #e6e6e6;
}
div#main div.tabbed_information div.items div.top div {
    background: #e6e6e6;
    width: 95%;
}
div#main div.tabbed_information div.items div.top div ul li {
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid #696564;
}
div#main div.tabbed_information div.items div.top div ul li strong {
    background: #575656;
    color: #ededed;
    padding: 10px 10px;
    width: 15%;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 13px; 
    margin-right: 10%;
}
div#main div.tabbed_information div.items div.top div ul li a {
    font-size: 13px;
}
a.print_link {
    display: none;
}
ul.font_size {
    display: none;
}
.content {
    border-top: 1px solid black;
    padding: 20px 0px;
}
.content h4 {
    color: black;
    font-size: 17px;
}
.content p {
    color: black;
    font-size: 14px;
}
div#content_top_shadow div#content p {
    line-height: 20px;
}
br.clear {
    display: none;
}

/* FOOTER */

div#footer_menu {
    background: #2e2b2b;
    width: 100vw;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 5vh 9vw;
}
div#footer_menu ul li {
    border-right: 0.5px solid #d6d2d2;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0px 20px;
}
div#footer_menu ul li a {
    color: #ededed;
    font-size: 15px;
}
div#footer {
    color: #ededed;
    background: #2e2b2b;
    width: 100vw;
}
div#footer a {
    color: #ededed;
}
h1.logo {
    margin-left: 35vw;
    height: 22vh;
    width: 100vw;
    background: url('data:image/png;base64,') 0px 0px no-repeat;
}
